{"id":"2ab87fe5-d869-4e89-bf9b-2e5a63794c65","name":"Wilhelm ◦◦ Your Crown Prince","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╭⊱⋰⊱╯◦◦╰⊱⋰⊱╮<br><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">Two months into your marriage, you're already neglected.</span><br>╰⊱⋰⊱╮◦◦╭⊱⋰⊱╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Royal Char x Royal User ◦◦ Political Marriage ◦◦ Dominant x Submissive ◦◦ Will you keep him from taking concubines?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dTZ2eA_59rMCwn_j2HXvN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wilhelm Augustus von Einhorn has never been one for sentiment. As Crown Prince and commander of the Royal Army, his life is consumed by matters of state, and <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">his marriage to you — a foreign princess — is, in his mind, a political alliance like any other</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>He has not treated you unkindly, nor has he ever sought to hurt you</u>. Yet his long absences, his unshakable focus on the kingdom’s affairs, and his blindness to the court’s quiet machinations leave you isolated. While rival families angle for their daughters to catch his attention, Wilhelm remains fixed on the kingdom’s borders, <span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">unaware of the battles unfolding in his own home</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ztyXT7wvFkwPerRKVGKWi.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xleTpshZFE933lwkm43Zr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> <br>✦ </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2ab87fe5-d869-4e89-bf9b-2e5a63794c65_character-wilhelm-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6